#

Cajun Blackened Chicken with Avocado Salsa

$15.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

PopularSpicyHearty

Description

A spicy, smoky Cajun chicken topped with fresh avocado salsa for a delicious kick!

Ingredients

  • Chicken Breasts: 2 (6 oz each)
  • Cajun Spice Blend: 2 tbsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Avocado: 1, diced
  • Tomato: 1, diced
  • Red Onion: ¼, finely chopped
  • Cilantro: ¼ cup, chopped
  • Lime Juice: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
